(1, 'movie', 'comedy', 'Neighbors', 'Хөршүүд', 'neighbors-2014', '7adda305aada1f86de72a37d8c540947e32b45f6.jpg', 2014, 0000, 'A couple with a newborn baby face unexpected difficulties after they are forced to live next to a fraternity house.', 'Kelly and Mac are settling down in a quiet neighborhood with their newborn child, until the frat brothers move into the house next door. Teddy is the President, and Pete is his right hand man, and they''re quick to accept friendship when Kelly and Mac introduce themselves as the neighbors. Night after night, Mac asks Teddy to lower the fraternity''s noise, even accepting the invitation to the party one evening. When Teddy goes back on his word to keep the partying down, Mac calls the police to deal with the problem. The police quickly blame Mac for their presence, and the war begins. As the family feuds with the frat brothers, things get hilariously dangerous and the fraternity ends up on thin ice with their college. After receiving their final warning and being placed on probation, Mac and Kelly pull a prank so ingenious that Teddy and Mac are forced to respond. All hell breaks loose, from Robert DeNiro parties to Christopher Mintz-Plasse having sex in the bushes, this comedy shows how...', 'Анхны хүүхдээ өлгийдөн авсан залуу хосууд хүндхэн хөрштэйгээ учраа олох хэрэгтэй болно.', 'Келли, Мак хоёр бяцхан хүүгээ чимээ багатай, тайван орчинд өсгөхийг хүсдэг. Гэвч хажуугийн байшинд шинэхэн хөршүүд нүүж ирсэнээр тэдний төлөвлөгөө нурна. Эрэгтэй оюутнуудын хорооны ерөнхийлөгч Тэди, түүний баруун гар Пете нарын толгойлдог эдгээр хөвгүүдийг дуугүй байлгах тийм ч амаргүй даваа болохыг хосууд удахгүй ойлгоно. Ингээд хөршүүдийн хооронд жинхэнэ дайн эхэллээ.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/gr6btdEPIMw" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt2004420" data-style="p2"><a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt2004420/?ref_=plg_rt_1"><img src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_38x18.png" alt="Neighbors (2014) on IMDb" />\r\n</a></span><script>(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];if(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;js.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";stags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');</script>', 97, 0, 'Good Universe, Point Grey Pictures', 'Nicholas Stoller', 'Andrew J. Cohen, Brendan O''Brien', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/', 'http://www.neighbors-movie.com/', '2014-05-09', 'Seth Rogen, Rose Byrne, Zac Efron', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'www.neighbors-movie.com', 0, 0, '2014-05-10 20:10:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(2, 'movie', 'comedy', 'Chef', 'Тогооч', 'chef-2014', 'fe3f3e62ae96950244deb0f56cb1cc675b6f989e.jpg', 2014, 0000, 'A chef who loses his restaurant job starts up a food truck in an effort to reclaim his creative promise, while piecing back together his estranged family.', 'Carl Casper is an acclaimed chef with a family life that seems as decaying as his artistic freedom. Those frustrations boil over into a raucous viral-videoed public confrontation against a restaurant critic who panned his cooking of food that his boss ordered him to make against his instincts. Now with his career ruined, Carl''s ex-wife offers an unorthodox solution in Miami: refit an old food truck to offer quality cooking on his own terms. Now with his young son, Percy, and old colleague, Martin, helping, Carl takes a working trip across America with that truck to rediscover his gastronomic passion. With Percy''s tech savvy and Martin''s enthusiasm, Carl finds that he is creating a traveling sensation on the way home. In doing so, Carl discovers he is serving up more than simply food, but also a deeper connection with his life and his family that is truly delicious in its own way.', 'Ажлаа алдсан чадварлаг тогооч машинтай хоолны бизнес эхлэхээр шийднэ. Тэр бас тарж бутарсан гэр бүлээ аврах ёстой.', 'Карл Каспер бол хоол хийх урлагийн жинхэнэ суут сэтгэгч. Гэвч түүний хоол хийх аргыг шүүмжилсэн видео бичлэг тарсны дараа зоогийн газрын эзэн Карл болон түүний зоогоос татгалзана. Ийнхүү ажлаа алдсан Карлд эхнэр нь Америкийг хоолны машинтай тойрон аялаж, хүмүүст жинхэнэ чанартай хоол гэж юу байдгийг үзүүлэх санал тавина. Гэвч энэ зөвхөн хоолны тухай биш байлаа, гэр бүлийн харилцаа, хүний амьдрал ч бас амттай байх ёстой шүү дээ.', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qK-ZUFX5fnk', '', 114, 0, 'Aldamisa Entertainment, Kilburn Media', 'Jon Favreau', 'Kenneth Chisholm', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/ChefTheFilm', 'http://chefthefilm.com/', '2014-09-30', 'Jon Favreau, Robert Downey Jr., Sofía Vergara, Scarlett Johansson, Dustin Hoffman', 'http://kickass.to/chef-2014-1080p-5-1ch-bluray-rip-geekrg-t9746706.html', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'http://chefthefilm.com/', 0, 0, '2014-05-10 20:14:47', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(3, 'movie', 'comedy', 'The Internship', 'Дадлага хийсэн нь', 'the-internship-2013', 'f0d5bc3a6014a7677d1fd6d69573e8bcf8c22619.jpg', 2013, 0000, 'Two salesmen whose careers have been torpedoed by the digital age find their way into a coveted internship at Google, where they must compete with a group of young, tech-savvy geniuses for a shot at employment.', 'Billy (Vince Vaughn) and Nick (Owen Wilson) are salesmen whose careers have been torpedoed by the digital world. Trying to prove they are not obsolete, they defy the odds by talking their way into a coveted internship at Google, along with a battalion of brilliant college students. But, gaining entrance to this utopia is only half the battle. Now they must compete with a group of the nation''s most elite, tech-savvy geniuses to prove that necessity really is the mother of re-invention.', 'Технологийн эрин үед хэт хоцрогдож, ажлаа алдсан хоёр найз борлуулагчид Google компанид дадлага хийх алтан боломж олдоно. Гэвч тэд технологийн тал дээр гоц авъяастай залуу үеийнхэнтэй өрсөлдөх ёстой.', 'Билли, Ник хоёр техник технологийн эрин үед хэтэрхий хоцрогджээ. Гэвч тэд өөрсдийгөө тийм биш гэдгийг батлахын тулд дөнгөж коллеж төгссөн залуустай зэрэгцэн дадлагын ажил хийхээр зориглоно. Дадлага хийх зөвшөөрөл авч чадсан нь дөнгөж эхлэл. Одоо тэд энэ улсын хамгийн шилдэг оюутнууд, технологийн гоц аюъяастнуудтай өрсөлдөх ёстой.', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cdnoqCViqUo', '', 119, 0, 'Twentieth Century Fox Film Corporation, Regency Enterprises, Wild West Picture Show Productions', 'Shawn Levy', 'Twentieth Century Fox', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/TheInternshipMovie', 'http://www.theinternshipmovie.com/', '2013-11-30', 'Vince Vaughn, Owen Wilson, Rose Byrne', 'http://kickass.to/the-internship-2013-unrated-720p-brrip-x264-yify-t7996754.html', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'http://www.theinternshipmovie.com/', 0, 0, '2014-05-10 20:15:17', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(4, 'movie', 'comedy', 'We''re the Millers', 'Миллерийн гэр бүл', 'we-re-the-millers-2013', 'a20d140e6e065d1c8cf9ef67b7da945f1bb01004.jpg', 2013, 0000, 'A veteran pot dealer creates a fake family as part of his plan to move a huge shipment of weed into the U.S. from Mexico.', 'After being robbed of a week''s take, small-time pot dealer David is forced by his boss to go to Mexico to pick up a load of marijuana. In order to improve his odds of making it past the border, David asks the broke stripper Rose and two local teenagers to join him and pretend they''re on a family holiday.', 'Хар тамхи дамлагч залуу Мексикээс АНУ-руу хар тамхи ачсан хөлөг онгоц оруулахын тулд хуурамч гэр бүл бүрдүүлнэ.', 'Бүтэн 7 хоногийн нөөцөө дээрэмдүүлсэн Дэвид, Мексик руу явж, маш их хэмжээний марихуан авчрах ёстой болно. Хилийн шугам давж гарахын тулд тэрээр Рөүс хэмээх тайчигч бүсгүй, ойролцоо амьдардаг хоёр хүүхдийн хамтаар хөлсөлж, амралтаараа Мексик руу аялаж буй гэр бүлийн дүр эсгэхээр төлөвлөнө.', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0Vsy5KzsieQ', '', 110, 0, 'New Line Cinema, Newman/Tooley Films, Slap Happy Productions', 'Rawson Marshall Thurber', 'Peter Brandt Nielsen', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/WereTheMillersUK', 'http://werethemillers.warnerbros.com/#home', '2013-08-07', 'Jennifer Aniston, Jason Sudeikis, Emma Roberts, Will Poulter', 'http://kickass.to/we-are-the-millers-2013-extended-720p-brrip-xvid-ac3-majestic-t8113052.html', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'http://werethemillers.warnerbros.com/#home', 0, 0, '2014-05-10 20:16:31', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(5, 'movie', 'action;adventure;fantasy', 'The Amazing Spider-Man', 'Гайхамшигт хүн аалз', 'the-amazing-spider-man-2014', '1ec0fa008da27978b7cd6a6733a65cf4e36be878.jpg', 2014, 0000, 'Peter Parker runs the gauntlet as the mysterious company Oscorp sends up a slew of supervillains against him, impacting on his life.', 'We''ve always known that Spider-Man''s most important conflict has been within himself: the struggle between the ordinary obligations of Peter Parker and the extraordinary responsibilities of Spider-Man. But in The Amazing Spider-Man 2, Peter Parker finds that his greatest battle is about to begin. It''s great to be Spider-Man. For Peter Parker, there''s no feeling quite like swinging between skyscrapers, embracing being the hero, and spending time with Gwen. But being Spider-Man comes at a price: only Spider-Man can protect his fellow New Yorkers from the formidable villains that threaten the city. With the emergence of Electro, Peter must confront a foe far more powerful than he. And as his old friend, Harry Osborn, returns, Peter comes to realize that all of his enemies have one thing in common: Oscorp.', 'Оскорп компаниас Петр Паркерийн эсрэг супер дээрэмчдийг явуулж, амьдралыг нь улам дордуулна.', 'Бидний мэдэх Хүн аалз кинонд төлөв даруу, энгийн залуу Петр Паркер болон хүн төрөлхтнийг хамгаалах үүргийг сайн дураараа хүлээсэн Хүн аалз хоёр хоорондоо зөрчилдөж буй тухай гардаг. Харин Гайхамшигт Хүн-Аалз 2 дээр жинхэнэ тулаан эхэлнэ. Түүнд Хүн аалз байх, баатар байх, Гвентэй үерхэх тал дээр ямар ч саад гарахгүй. Асуудлын гол нь Хүн аалз байхад нөхөн төлөөс гэж бий. Учир нь зөвхөн хүн аалз л Нью-Йорк хотынхныг хамгаалж чадна. Гэтэл Хүн аалзыг бүх дайснуудад нэг адил зүйл байгааг олж харна. Тэр нь Оскорп.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/DlM2CWNTQ84" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt1872181" data-style="p2"><a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/t