(25, 'movie', 'horror', 'Ouija', '', 'ouija-2014', '8c2a8528ffc8a22101de1bf7aa4666060dab250e.jpg', 2014, 0000, 'A group of friends must confront their most terrifying fears when they awaken the dark powers of an ancient spirit board.', 'A girl is mysteriously killed after recording herself playing with an ancient Ouija Board, which leads to a close group of friends to investigate this board. They later find out that some things aren''t meant to be played with, especially the ''other side''.', 'Эртний сүнс дуудах хэрэгслээр харын хүчийг сэрээсэн хэсэг залуус сэтгэлийнхээ гүн дэх хамгийн аймшигт айдастай нүүр тулах болно.', 'Оуйжа нэрт эртний тоглоомоор тоглож байгаад өөд болсон охины дотны найзууд нь хэргийн учрыг тайлахаар тоглоомыг үргэлжлүүлнэ. Гэвч тэд зарим зүйлсээр тоглож болдоггүйг ойлгоно. Жишээ нь нөгөө ертөнц.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/QPFK4ezZzIA" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt1204977" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1204977/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Ouija (2014) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 89, 18, 'Stiles White', 'Stiles White', 'Juliet Snowden (screenplay), Stiles White (screenplay)', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/ouijamovie', 'http://www.ouijamovieintl.com/ww/', '2014-10-24', 'Olivia Cooke, Ana Coto, Daren Kagasoff', 'http://kickass.to/ouija-2014-720p-first-eng-hdcam-x264-pimp4003-t9799225.html', 0, 11, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 0, 0, '2014-11-03 14:17:30', '0000-00-00 00:00