(35, 'movie', 'fantasy', 'The Hobbit: The Battle of the Five Armies', '', 'the-hobbit-the-battle-of-the-five-armies-2014', 'cb293ceed8601db8e4725ae24ed85130bda4ca8e.jpg', 2014, 0000, 'Bilbo and Company are forced to be embraced in a war against an armed flock of combatants and the terrifying Smaug from acquiring a kingdom of treasure and obliterating all of Middle-Earth.', 'Mere seconds after the events of "Desolation", Bilbo and Company continue to claim a mountain of treasure that was guarded long ago: But with Gandalf the Grey also facing some formidable foes of his own, the Hobbit is outmatched when the brutal army of orcs led by Azog the Defiler returns. But with other armies such as the elves and the men of Lake-Town, which are unsure to be trusted, are put to the ultimate test when Smaug''s wrath, Azog''s sheer strength, and Sauron''s force of complete ends attack. All in all, the trusted armies have two choices: unite or die. But even worse, Bilbo gets put on a knife edge and finds himself fighting with Hobbit warfare with all of his might for his dwarf-friends, as the hope for Middle-Earth is all put in Bilbo''s hands. The one "precious" thing to end it all', '', '', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/cOHJQkBtMWs" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '', 210, 16, ' New Line Cinema, Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer (MGM),', 'Peter Jackson', 'Fran Walsh (screenplay), Philippa Boyens', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/TheHobbitMovie', 'http://www.thehobbitblog.com/', '0020-12-17', 'Ian McKellen, Martin Freeman, Richard Armitage ', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 'imdb.com', 0, 0, '2014-11-06 04:28:17', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(36, 'movie', 'biography;drama', 'The Theory of Everything', 'The Theory of Everything', 'the-theory-of-everything-2014', '0bd8778d8a6a6cd4eae671c589a5bc7b68acab49.jpg', 2014, 0000, 'A look at the relationship between the famous physicist Stephen Hawking and his wife.', 'This is the extraordinary story of one of the world''s greatest living minds, the renowned astrophysicist Stephen Hawking, who falls deeply in love with fellow Cambridge student Jane Wilde. Once a healthy, active young man, Hawking received an earth-shattering diagnosis at 21 years of age. With Jane fighting tirelessly by his side, Stephen embarks on his most ambitious scientific work, studying the very thing he now has precious little of - time. Together, they defy impossible odds, breaking new ground in medicine and science, and achieving more than they could ever have dreamed', 'Энэхүү киног алдарт физикч Стефэн Ховкинг болон түүний эхнэрийн тухай бодит түүхээс сэдэвлэн бүтээжээ. ', 'Хүн төрөлхтний түүхийн хамгийн агуу сэтгэгчдийн нэг астрофизикч Стефэн Ховкингийн тухай гайхамшигт түүхийг энд өгүүлнэ. Стефэн Кэмбриджийн их сургуульд суралцаж байхдаа эхнэр Жэйн Вилдетэй танилцдаг. Эрүүл чийрэг, идэвх зүтгэлтэй яюсан Стефэн 21 насандаа аймшигт мэдээ хүлээн авдаг. Тиймээс Стефэн багахан үлдсэн амьдралынхаа эцсийн мөчүүдэд шинжлэх ухаанд шинэ нээлт хийхээр уйгагүй хөдөлмөрлөнө. Түүний дэргэд эхнэр Жэйн нь бууж өгөлгүй түүнийг дэмжиж, хосууд хамтдаа зүтгэсээр шинжлэх ухаанд шинэ салбарыг гаргаж ирж, өөрсдийн мөрөөдөж ч байгаагүй тийм өндөр амжилтанд хүрдэг. ', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/LUayjO_KgsQ" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt2980516" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt2980516/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="The Theory of Everything (2014) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<scr